reviewText: This is among the funniest finds from the internet, so fresh and original, with none too subtle social commentary.  KEEP THOSE DANG RAISINS AWAY FROM MY COOKIES!

Finally Shawks has made its way to dvd, This is a best of set and a better set is due out soon (got word from the animator himself) But this set is very impressive. Shawks is a short web animated serries about a crew of pre-schoolers who slaughter grown men and women whom they belive are sharks (or shawks as they say it). This is a good buy but unless your not serriously into the whole sick and twisted cartoons you would be better off buying spike and mike or best of the web vol 2.
